#: parking_permits/templates/emails/expiration_remind.html:8
msgid "Your parking permit expires at"
msgstr "Pysäköintitunnuksesi voimassaoloaika päättyy"

#: parking_permits/templates/emails/expiration_remind.html:9
msgid ""
"You can renew your permit by logging in to the service and selecting 'Extend "
"parking permit'."
msgstr ""
"Voit uusia tunnuksen kirjautumalla palveluun ja valitsemalla 'Jatka "
"pysäköintitunnuksen voimassaoloa'."

#: parking_permits/templates/emails/permit_created.html:8
msgid "Thank you for your order!"
msgstr "Kiitos tilauksestasi!"

#: parking_permits/templates/emails/permit_created.html:9
#: parking_permits/templates/emails/temporary_vehicle_activated.html:21
#: parking_permits/templates/emails/temporary_vehicle_deactivated.html:21
msgid ""
"The parking permit is electronic and parking permit enforcers will identify "
"permit validity based on your vehicle licence plate number."
msgstr ""
"Pysäköintitunnus on sähköinen ja pysäköinninvalvonta tunnistaa voimassa "
"olevan tunnuksen ajoneuvosi rekisterinumeron perusteella."

#: parking_permits/templates/emails/permit_ended.html:8
msgid "Your parking permit validity period has ended at"
msgstr "Pysäköintitunnuksesi voimassaoloaika päättyi"

#: parking_permits/templates/emails/permit_ended.html:9
msgid ""
"If you want to continue permit usage, you will need to make a new order."
msgstr "Mikäli haluat jatkaa tunnuksen käyttöä tulee sinun tehdä uusi tilaus."

#: parking_permits/templates/emails/permit_extended.html:8
#: parking_permits/templates/emails/permit_updated.html:8
msgid ""
"Thank you for your order! The parking permit is electronic and parking "
"permit enforcers will identify permit validity based on your vehicle licence "
"plate number."
msgstr ""
"Kiitos tilauksestasi! Pysäköintitunnus on sähköinen ja pysäköinninvalvonta "
"tunnistaa voimassa olevan tunnuksen ajoneuvosi rekisterinumeron perusteella."

#: parking_permits/templates/emails/refund_accepted.html:8
msgid ""
"Your refund has been accepted and will appear on the account you reported "
"within about a week"
msgstr ""
"Palautus on hyväksytty ja näkyy ilmoittamallasi tilillä noin viikon kuluessa."

#: parking_permits/templates/emails/refund_accepted.html:12
#: parking_permits/templates/emails/refund_created.html:12
msgid "Total refundable amount"
msgstr "Palautettava summa yhteensä"

#: parking_permits/templates/emails/refund_accepted.html:13
#: parking_permits/templates/emails/refund_created.html:13
msgid "incl. VAT"
msgstr "sis. ALV"

#: parking_permits/templates/emails/refund_created.html:8
msgid ""
"You are entitled to a refund and it has been registered. You will receive a "
"separate notification when the return has been approved."
msgstr ""
"Olet oikeutettu palautukseen ja se on otettu käsittelyyn. Saat erillisen "
"ilmoituksen, kun palautus on hyväksytty."

#: parking_permits/templates/emails/temporary_vehicle_activated.html:8
